---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-6">Insights</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300/90 mb-10">Stories and testimonials from Lagos, Nigeria—more coming soon.</p>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/70 ring-1 ring-slate-700 p-6 shadow-md">
        <blockquote class="text-slate-200">“The training session helped our team adopt better web practices in one week.”</blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-400">— ICT Coordinator, Surulere, Lagos</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/70 ring-1 ring-slate-700 p-6 shadow-md">
        <blockquote class="text-slate-200">“Predictive insights from our sales data identified our best channels. Revenue improved.”</blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-400">— Operations Lead, Yaba, Lagos</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/70 ring-1 ring-slate-700 p-6 shadow-md">
        <blockquote class="text-slate-200">“Landing page + WhatsApp bot gave us steady qualified leads without extra ad spend.”</blockquote>
        <figcaption class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-400">— Entrepreneur, Victoria Island, Lagos</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
